2:16:27.304 --> 2:16:29.390
[Willard] They were going to make me
a major for this,

2:16:30.766 --> 2:16:33.227
and I wasn't even
in their fucking army anymore.

2:16:36.063 --> 2:16:37.898
Everybody wanted me to do it,

2:16:39.733 --> 2:16:41.068
him most of all.

2:16:42.778 --> 2:16:44.363
I felt like he was up there,

2:16:45.197 --> 2:16:47.157
waiting for me to take the pain away.

2:16:50.452 --> 2:16:52.496
He just wanted to go out like a soldier,

2:16:53.831 --> 2:16:54.832
standing up,

2:16:55.999 --> 2:16:59.545
not like some poor, wasted,
rag-assed renegade.

2:17:03.340 --> 2:17:05.300
Even the jungle wanted him dead,

2:17:06.719 --> 2:17:09.304
